{
    "pages": [
        {
            "texts": [
                {
                    "text": "\"Nous parlons à travers les veines du cosmos, à travers l'éther vibrant qui unit toutes choses.",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_1.mp3",
                    "order": 0,
                    "from": "top",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "1",
                        "gridRowStart": "1"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "text": "Nous avons vu ton cœur, pur, ta foi inébranlable, ta volonté de pierre. Et nous te saluons.\"",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_2.mp3",
                    "order": 1,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "2",
                        "gridRowStart": "3"
                    },
                    "coloredLetters": [
                        {
                            "from": 83,
                            "to": 91,
                            "color": "#8B0000"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "text": "\"Tu as lu notre Livre, tu as appris nos mots, tu as tracé nos symboles avec une main sûre et dévouée.",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_3.mp3",
                    "order": 2,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "2",
                        "gridRowStart": "9"
                    },
                    "coloredLetters": [
                        {
                            "from": 16,
                            "to": 20,
                            "color": "#866121"
                        },
                        {
                            "from": 0,
                            "to": 150,
                            "color": "#fff"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "text": "Tu cherches la vérité, et tu as bien raison. Car la vérité libère, Céleste, elle libère de la peur, de l'ignorance et du mensonge.\"",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_4.mp3",
                    "order": 3,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "2",
                        "gridRowStart": "11"
                    },
                    "coloredLetters": [
                        {
                            "from": 121,
                            "to": 128,
                            "color": "#432373"
                        },
                        {
                            "from": 0,
                            "to": 130,
                            "color": "#fff"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "arts": [
                {
                    "path": "/sound/page_1/celeste6.png",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/artwork.mp3",
                    "order": 2,
                    "style": {
                        "margin": "auto",
                        "padding": "3rem",
                        "gridColumn": "span 8 / span 8",
                        "gridColumnStart": "1",
                        "gridRowStart": "5"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "texts": [
                {
                    "text": "\"Et pourtant, Céleste, ta quête de vérité t'a été refusée. Tu vis dans un monde de mensonges, d'omissions et de demi-vérités.",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_5.mp3",
                    "order": 4,
                    "from": "top",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "2",
                        "gridRowStart": "1"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "text": "Les Ascendants, ceux qui prétendent détenir la sagesse, te cachent la vraie nature de l'Essence, la vraie nature de notre Création.\"",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_6.mp3",
                    "order": 5,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "1",
                        "gridRowStart": "3"
                    },
                    "coloredLetters": [
                        {
                            "from": 4,
                            "to": 13,
                            "color": "#8B0000"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "text": "\"Ces barrières autour de ton monde, Céleste, elles n'ont pas été construites pour te protéger, mais pour te maintenir enfermée, ignorant la vérité.",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_7.mp3",
                    "order": 6,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "2",
                        "gridRowStart": "5"
                    },
                    "coloredLetters": [
                        {
                            "from": 118,
                            "to": 126,
                            "color": "#666"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "text": "Mais il est temps maintenant de lever le voile. Le moment est venu pour toi de renverser ces murs d'illusions, de libérer ton monde de l'ignorance et de la manipulation.",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_8.mp3",
                    "order": 7,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "2",
                        "gridRowStart": "8"
                    },
                    "coloredLetters": [
                        {
                            "from": 156,
                            "to": 168,
                            "color": "#C0AFE2"
                        },
                        {
                            "from": 0,
                            "to": 170,
                            "color": "#fff"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "text": "Nous te demandons, Céleste, de continuer ta révolution, de briser ces chaînes de mensonges, et d'ouvrir ton monde à la vérité. Car c'est dans cette vérité que se trouve la véritable liberté, le véritable salut.\"",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_9.mp3",
                    "order": 8,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 6 / span 6",
                        "gridColumnStart": "2",
                        "gridRowStart": "11"
                    },
                    "coloredLetters": [
                        {
                            "from": 194,
                            "to": 210,
                            "color": "#ffd700"
                        },
                        {
                            "from": 0,
                            "to": 220,
                            "color": "#fff"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "arts": [
                {
                    "path": "/sound/page_1/premiers-etres.png",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/artwork.mp3",
                    "order": 7,
                    "style": {
                        "margin": "auto",
                        "padding": "3rem",
                        "gridColumn": "span 8 / span 8",
                        "gridColumnStart": "1",
                        "gridRowStart": "6"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "texts": [
                {
                    "text": "\"N'aie pas peur, Céleste. Nous sommes avec toi.",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_10.mp3",
                    "order": 10,
                    "from": "top",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 4 / span 4",
                        "gridColumnStart": "3",
                        "gridRowStart": "4"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "text": "Nous t'attendons de l'autre côté du voile.\"",
                    "sound": "/sound/page_1/voice_11.mp3",
                    "order": 11,
                    "from": "bottom",
                    "style": {
                        "gridColumn": "span 4 / span 4",
                        "gridColumnStart": "3",
                        "gridRowStart": "8"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
        }
    ]
